    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Android-端关于WebView历史记录进退栈遇到的坑"><a href="#Android-端关于WebView历史记录进退栈遇到的坑" class="headerlink" title="Android 端关于WebView历史记录进退栈遇到的坑"></a>Android 端关于WebView历史记录进退栈遇到的坑</h1><p> 因为要做一个类似于Chrome浏览器那样的功能，即有多个Tab标签网页，其中有一个功能需要实现，就是webview中的历史进退栈，即记录用户在同一个tab上面访问的网站的进退栈，像下一页，或者上一页的进退栈信息的记录。而webview为我们提供了copyBackForwardList()方法，可以拿到目前webview记录的进退栈信息, 该方法返回WebBackForwardList的一个对象，我们看一下WebBackForwardList的源码（我去除了注释）：</p><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">WebBackForwardList</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">Cloneable</span>, <span class="hljs-title">Serializable</span> </span>&#123;        <span class="hljs-meta">@Nullable</span>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> WebHistoryItem <span class="hljs-title">getCurrentItem</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">getCurrentIndex</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;        <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> WebHistoryItem <span class="hljs-title">getItemAtIndex</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> index)</span></span>;    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">getSize</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;        <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> WebBackForwardList <span class="hljs-title">clone</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;&#125;</code></pre><p>其中可以看到WebBackForwardList中存储的类型是WebHistoryItem，我们再看下WebHistoryItem的源码（同样去除注释）：</p><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">WebHistoryItem</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">Cloneable</span> </span>&#123;        <span class="hljs-meta">@SystemApi</span>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Deprecated</span>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">getId</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> String <span class="hljs-title">getUrl</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> String <span class="hljs-title">getOriginalUrl</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> String <span class="hljs-title">getTitle</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;    <span class="hljs-meta">@Nullable</span>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> Bitmap <span class="hljs-title">getFavicon</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">abstract</span> WebHistoryItem <span class="hljs-title">clone</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;&#125;</code></pre><p>在这里我们可以看到记录着url，title、favicon等信息都有。下面是我随便浏览了几个页面调用copyBackForwardList的结果：<br><img src="1.png"></p><p>嗯，就用webview的这一套来记录进退历史记录吧。可是仔细一想，那如果我退出程序了这些进退栈还保留着吗？通过自己的亲测，如果webview被销毁，copyBackForwardList中的数据就会丢失。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
